    public class RuleBaseImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements RuleBase
    An implementation of the model object 'Rule Base'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Violate Type
    • VUpper Limit PU
    • VLower Limit PU
    • Apply Rule Base
    • Rule Sets
